ygData.subject: Are there ANY half-elf warriors besides me?
ygData.msgSnippet: Just wondering if there are any half-elf warriors out there.  I am level 5 now and am hanging around with a high elf wizard and a wood elf ranger (Both level
ygData.messageBody:
Just wondering if there are any half-elf warriors out there. I am level 5 now and am hanging around with a high elf wizard and a wood elf ranger (Both level 8). We can do some serious damage, but it is tough to know what I should be working on since no one else seems to match my race/class. ANY info you can give would be good. Also, what armor can I use? I haven't found any near Kelethin of Felwithe that is compatible with me. Oh well, not much near those cities can really put the hurt on me anyway, unless I got grouped up on by some Orc Centurions, even they don't usually stand a chance when I fight the one's that con white to me (or yellow sometimes) and I get the alone.

Xangor
